Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:18.71,mianze,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,500)}翻译:あおい アナザ 校对:初夏 后期:乌贼贼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想見到你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:31.85,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&HF3727B&\3c&HFFFFFF&}M&S
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無論如何都有想告訴你的事 所以就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是愛的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10萬日元？只是之前那天做的工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 聘請我是很貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.26,0:01:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你難道付不起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我不久前買了「魔法少女小桃香」的Blu-ray BOX
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在手頭有點緊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:02:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話就用你的身體來支付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 小瀨奈真H
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要溫柔點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓你償還之前對我的侮辱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說你從最開始就打算這樣做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好反省你侮辱我的罪過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 看招 再來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣啊 愛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可能是瀨奈的力氣不大 不是很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說打的力度剛好火辣辣的 有點舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小瀨奈布丁一般的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軟軟的 觸感也非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是我打得不夠用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.32,0:03:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別靠近我 你這個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那傢伙的助手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.92,0:03:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快想想辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那個我不太想和他扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你繼續鞭撻我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就由我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然敢在那種人身邊工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:07.42,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H0CADF5&}對不起 對不起 見張
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近可愛的吉祥物角色好像挺受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也畫個出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我漫畫的風格不太符合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挺喜歡這類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上畫出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.90,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H7F70F5&}吉祥物角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足須小姐 你喜歡什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢 我現在有點喜歡這個「懶懶熊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個非常可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個治癒的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得足須小姐你更可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你不要開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 先畫個這種感覺的角色就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs25\fn@ZhunYuan\frz-90\pos(193,273)}好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:04:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你當我是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs25\fn@ZhunYuan\frz-90\pos(193,273)}哎嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs25\fn@ZhunYuan\frz-86\pos(174,322)}內褲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胖次君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs25\fn@ZhunYuan\frz-85\pos(215,341)}胖次丘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個怎麼樣呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個內褲和禮帽的不搭配組合 絕妙的超現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\fs25\fn@ZhunYuan\frz-78\move(189.025,379.335,268.8,398.332,16,225)}胸罩喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師真是個天才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫多些 請再多畫一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我畫的話 我說什麼你都會聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色色的事也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:50.27,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&HB8004B&}說的也是啊 愛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多我想要周邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道會有這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:05.16,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H83FF8A&\3c&HFFFFFF&}胸罩喵登場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 你好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為我這樣就會滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師和我一起做周邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還能繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師你好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做…做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足須小姐 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲奈小姐的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足須小姐 你這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fad(0,0)\c&H000000&\pos(600,385)}請疼愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後啊 足須小姐她很過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸罩喵…真正的胸罩喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微也搭理我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足須小姐 你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後 我也輸給了它可愛的魅力 就把它飼養了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H2D2F51&\bord0\fs25\fn@ZhunYuan\frz-75\pos(246,121)}請多多指教 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.67,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H2D2F51&}喵 胸罩喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這周也辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 多虧你才能趕出稿子來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛徒真的從以前開始就喜歡拖到臨交稿前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 見張小姐和老師有多久交情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外的有點長…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:40.32,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&HF81DC4&}17歲的見張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見張你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天拿漫畫去出版社投稿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是他們說總之你畫的太爛了 不適合做漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近都沒有什麼好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前陣子買的豐胸器也完全沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還畫的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.60,0:09:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害！可以給我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明坐你旁邊都沒有和你好好說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是叫愛徒同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嚇我一跳啊 你居然畫的這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也嚇一跳啊 音砂同學會跟我搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為音砂同學你很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛徒同學你才是更棒啊 畫得這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天我要把自己喜歡的事物通過漫畫傳達給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這是一件非常困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在碰壁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天從音砂同學那裏得到鼓勵了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音砂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會為你打氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望愛徒同學能堅持你喜歡的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 愛徒同學喜歡的事物是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜歡內褲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧對吧 很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個絲蕾邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個條紋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏啊 這個線條很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是畢業之後跟他說我當編輯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就過來投稿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當年我太年輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的發生了很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.16,0:00:02.85,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}そのままだっていいだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:04.19,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}言わないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:07.38,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ダメ 内緒だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.54,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}好きは正しい！うえに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:22.18,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}好きは強い！強い！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:27.86,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}正直な自分が一番
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:30.59,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}だけど君の心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.31,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どこ向いてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:38.42,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}私の事ちゃんと見てないの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:44.32,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}近すぎて  遠くなるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.72,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}恋への階段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:51.83,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}私は登ろうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:54.58,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}決めて！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.75,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}純粋なフヅユンブシ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:03.76,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ときめきを持て余してると 気づいた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:06.00,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ややや 困るの！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:08.75,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}そのままだっていいだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:12.42,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君らしくていいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:16.03,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}なんて  いつか言いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:18.55,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}まだ言わないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.16,0:00:02.85,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.91,0:00:04.19,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我是不會說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:07.38,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不行 這是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.54,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因為喜歡就是真理!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:22.18,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}才會越來越喜歡你!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:27.86,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坦率的自己才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:30.59,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:33.31,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}又將在哪落葉歸根呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:38.42,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你有好好的正視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:44.32,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}看近卻遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.72,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}這就是通往戀愛的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:51.83,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我要迎階而上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:54.58,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}決定吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.75,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}純粹的雜質
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:03.76,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}意識到自己小鹿亂撞不可抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:06.00,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}呀呀呀  該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:08.75,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:12.42,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你做你自己就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:16.03,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}這些總有一天會說出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:18.55,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是現在還不會說哦

